  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbf, \u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Prohibition on the use of rice and paddy for animal feed production",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Consumer Affairs Authority has issued a special gazette notification banning the direct or indirect use of rice or paddy for animal feed production.",
        "According to the Gazette notification, all activities such as selling or storing and transporting rice for animal feed production are prohibited.",
        "This Special Gazette has been issued with effect from the 24th of this month under the Consumer Affairs Authority Act No. 9 of 2003.",
        "Accordingly, the import, sale, distribution or storage of rice or paddy directly by any importer, manufacturer, trader or distributor for animal feed production or any other raw material shall be prohibited.",
        "Meanwhile, the Consumer Affairs Authority (CAA) has said it will continue to crack down on those selling rice at higher than maximum retail prices."
      ],
